::DarkMouse::
She woke up in the CR chamber fully healed.  She took a step out and 
looked around the room.

::KitKat::
The sensors in the lab were set off and notified KitKat that there 
was movement in the lab.

"Destructor, I believe that bot that you brought in is now awake and 
moving. Please see to it that she doesn't go anywhere. Thank you."

She looked at Aracnia and Cyber Claw. "This way to the conference 
room."  she walked down the hall and stopped at the doorway to the 
large room. "Please, make yourselves comfortable."
